OL,3,C'Forever chemicals' found in common UK
OL,4,Cfruit and vegetables
OL,6,FThe chemicals can accumulate in the
OL,7,Fbodies of living organisms and have
OL,8,Fbeen linked to severe health
OL,9,Fconditions, ITV News Science
OL,10,FCorrespondent Martin Stew reports
OL,12,FCommon UK , and spices have been found
OL,13,Fto be contaminated with long-lasting
OL,14,Ftoxins known as "forever chemicals",
OL,15,Fprompting alarm over potential impacts
OL,16,Fon public health among campaigners.
