OL,3,C'Forever chemicals' found in common UK
OL,4,Cfruit and vegetables
OL,6,FPFA chemicals - also known as forever
OL,7,Fchemicals because they can take
OL,8,Fcenturies to break down in the
OL,9,Fenvironment - used in some pesticides,
OL,10,Fwere identified in a range of foods in
OL,11,F2022, according to results from the
OL,12,Flatest government testing.
OL,14,FPFAs can accumulate in the bodies of
OL,15,Fliving organisms and have been linked
OL,16,Fto severe health conditions.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/9
