OL,3,C'Forever chemicals' found in common UK
OL,4,Cfruit and vegetables
OL,6,FMore than 3,300 samples of food and
OL,7,Fdrink available in the UK supply chain
OL,8,Fwere tested for residues of around 401
OL,9,Fpesticides in 2022, according to a
OL,10,Freport from the Environment
OL,11,FDepartment's advisory committee on
OL,12,Fpesticide residues (PRiF).
OL,14,FThe Pesticide Action Network UK (Pan
OL,15,FUK), which analysed the test results,
OL,16,Ffound strawberries to be the worst
OL,17,Foffender, with 95% of 120 test samples
OL,18,Fcontaining PFA pesticides.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/9
