OL,6,FWant a quick and expert briefing on
OL,7,Fthe biggest news stories? Listen to
OL,8,Four latest podcasts to find out What
OL,9,FYou Need To Know...
OL,11,FMeanwhile, 1.8% of the samples
OL,12,Fcontained a pesticide residue above
OL,13,Fthis legal level.
OL,15,FThe report said the UK's Health and
OL,16,FSafety Executive (HSE) conducts a risk
OL,17,Fassessment of all pesticide residues
OL,18,Ffound in the testing programme and
OL,19,Ftakes further action if risks to
OL,20,Fhealth are identified.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/9
