OL,6,F"It is useful to note, even when a
OL,7,Ffood contains a residue above the MRL,
OL,8,FHSE rarely finds any likely risk to
OL,9,Fthe health of the people who have
OL,10,Featen the food," it said.
OL,12,FHowever, Pan UK said MRLs do not
OL,13,Fguarantee the quantity of pesticide
OL,14,Ffound in the food is safe and do not
OL,15,Ftake into account the many other
OL,16,Froutes of potential PFA exposure, such
OL,17,Fas plastic food packaging, drinking
OL,18,Fwater and a wide range of household
OL,19,Fproducts.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/9
