OL,3,C'Forever chemicals' found in common UK
OL,4,Cfruit and vegetables
OL,6,FNick Mole, from Pan UK, said: "Given
OL,7,Fthe growing body of evidence linking
OL,8,FPFAs to serious diseases such as
OL,9,Fcancer, it is deeply worrying that UK
OL,10,Fconsumers are being left with no
OL,11,Fchoice but to ingest these chemicals,
OL,12,Fsome of which may remain in their
OL,13,Fbodies long into the future.
OL,15,F"We urgently need to develop a better
OL,16,Funderstanding of the health risks
OL,17,Fassociated with ingesting these
OL,18,F'forever chemicals' and do everything
OL,19,Fwe can to exclude them from the food
OL,20,Fchain."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/9
