OL,6,FPan UK is urging the government to ban
OL,7,Fthe 25 PFA pesticides currently in use
OL,8,Fin Britain, six of which are
OL,9,Fclassified as "highly hazardous".
OL,11,FThe organisation said ministers should
OL,12,Falso increase support for farmers to
OL,13,Fhelp them end their reliance on
OL,14,Fchemicals and adopt safer, more
OL,15,Fsustainable alternatives.
OL,17,FITV News has contacted Defra and HSE
OL,18,Ffor comment.
